threshold, or weighted methods}
\item{\code{\link[=tessera_communities]{tessera_communities()}}}{Step 3a: Detect community structure using
Leiden, spectral, or Neighbor-Joining}
\item{\code{\link[=tessera_divergence]{tessera_divergence()}}}{Step 3b: Quantify regime divergence across
temporal bins}
}
